href=\"/blog\">Blog</a><a class=\"hover:text-white hover:text-shadow transition-all relative after:content-[&#x27;&#x27;] after:absolute after:w-full after:scale-x-0 after:h-0.5 after:bottom-0 after:left-0 after:bg-accent-400 after:origin-bottom-right after:transition-transform hover:after:scale-x-100 hover:after:origin-bottom-left\" href=\"/contact\">Contact</a></div><div class=\"hidden lg:flex items-center space-x-3 bg-white px-5 py-2.5 rounded-xl shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(255,255,255,0.1)] group cursor-pointer hover:shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(255,255,255,0.2)] transition-shadow\"><span class=\"text-2xl group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform origin-center\">📞</span><div><div class=\"text-[10px] text-surface-500 font-extrabold uppercase tracking-widest\">Need Help? Talk to Experts</div><a href=\"tel:614-926-0787\" class=\"text-sm font-extrabold text-brand-900 hover:text-accent-600 transition-colors\">614-926-0787</a></div></div><button class=\"lg:hidden text-brand-50 hover:text-white p-2\" aria-label=\"Menu\"><svg class=\"w-8 h-8\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M4 6h16M4 12h16M4 18h16\"></path></svg></button></div></header><div class=\"min-h-screen flex flex-col\"><div class=\"bg-white text-gray-900 min-h-screen\"><section class=\"relative pt-32 pb-24 px-4 bg-[#0d1b2a] overflow-hidden flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center min-h-[350px]\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 z-0 opacity-20\" style=\"background-image:url(&#x27;https://www.transparenttextures.com/patterns/cubes.png&#x27;)\"></div><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-[#0d1b2a]/80 to-[#0d1b2a]\"></div><div class=\"relative z-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto\"><div class=\"text-gray-300 font-medium mb-4 flex items-center justify-center gap-2 text-sm uppercase tracking-wider\"><a class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\" href=\"/\">Home</a><span>›</span><span class=\"text-[#ff7340]\">Our Team</span></div><h1 class=\"text-5xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold text-white mb-6 tracking-tight\">Meet the Experts</h1><p class=\"text-xl text-gray-300 font-light max-w-2xl mx-auto\">The certified entomologists and experienced technicians behind our pest control solutions and educational content.</p></div></section><section class=\"py-24 px-4 bg-surface-50\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto\"><div class=\"text-center mb-16\"><h2 class=\"text-4xl font-extrabold text-surface-900 mb-4\">Our Authors &amp; Leadership</h2><p class=\"text-lg text-surface-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto\">Our content is written and reviewed by industry veterans who spend their days in the field. Get to know the team dedicated to keeping your property pest-free.</p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8\"><div class=\"bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-xl shadow-brand-900/5 border border-gray-100 hover:-translate-y-2 transition-transform duration-300 group\"><div class=\"w-24 h-24 mx-auto rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-500 to-brand-700 text-white font-bold text-3xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 shadow-lg transform group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform\">RB</div><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-surface-900 text-center mb-1\">Dr. Robert Baty</h3><p class=\"text-[#ff7340] font-medium text-center text-sm mb-4 uppercase tracking-wide\">Chief Entomologist &amp; Lead Author</p><div class=\"w-12 h-1 bg-gray-100 mx-auto mb-4 rounded-full\"></div><p class=\"text-surface-600 text-center text-sm leading-relaxed\">With over 20 years of experience in structural pest control, Dr. Baty oversees all treatment protocols and writes our in-depth pest prevention guides.</p></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-xl shadow-brand-900/5 border border-gray-100 hover:-translate-y-2 transition-transform duration-300 group\"><div class=\"w-24 h-24 mx-auto rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-accent-400 to-accent-600 text-white font-bold text-3xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 shadow-lg transform group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform\">SJ</div><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-surface-900 text-center mb-1\">Sarah Jenkins</h3><p class=\"text-[#ff7340] font-medium text-center text-sm mb-4 uppercase tracking-wide\">Senior Operations Manager</p><div class=\"w-12 h-1 bg-gray-100 mx-auto mb-4 rounded-full\"></div><p class=\"text-surface-600 text-center text-sm leading-relaxed\">Sarah ensures that our nationwide fleet of technicians is always ready to respond to emergencies 24/7. She contributes to our customer service blog.</p></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-xl shadow-brand-900/5 border border-gray-100 hover:-translate-y-2 transition-transform duration-300 group\"><div class=\"w-24 h-24 mx-auto rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-blue-700 text-white font-bold text-3xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 shadow-lg transform group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform\">MC</div><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-surface-900 text-center mb-1\">Michael Chen</h3><p class=\"text-[#ff7340] font-medium text-center text-sm mb-4 uppercase tracking-wide\">Wildlife Control Specialist</p><div class=\"w-12 h-1 bg-gray-100 mx-auto mb-4 rounded-full\"></div><p class=\"text-surface-600 text-center text-sm leading-relaxed\">Michael is our resident expert on humane wildlife removal and exclusion. He regularly authors articles on how to animal-proof residential properties.</p></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 shadow-xl shadow-brand-900/5 border border-gray-100 hover:-translate-y-2 transition-transform duration-300 group\"><div class=\"w-24 h-24 mx-auto rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-[#b18c95] to-brand-900 text-white font-bold text-3xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 shadow-lg transform group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform\">ER</div><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-surface-900 text-center mb-1\">Elena Rodriguez</h3><p class=\"text-[#ff7340] font-medium text-center text-sm mb-4 uppercase tracking-wide\">Termite &amp; WDO Inspector</p><div class=\"w-12 h-1 bg-gray-100 mx-auto mb-4 rounded-full\"></div><p class=\"text-surface-600 text-center text-sm leading-relaxed\">Elena has conducted over 5,000 termite inspections. Her technical writing focuses on early detection of wood-destroying organisms.</p></div></div></div></section><section class=\"py-20 px-4 bg-white border-t border-gray-100\"><div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center bg-brand-50 rounded-3xl p-12 border border-brand-100\"><h3 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-surface-900 mb-4\">Our Editorial Promise</h3><p class=\"text-surface-700 text-lg mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto\">Every blog post and service guide published on batyspestcontrol is rigorously fact-checked by our certified entomology team. We believe in providing scientifically accurate, practical, and safe advice for all your pest concerns.</p><a class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-[#0d1b2a] text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-bold hover:bg-[#ff7340] hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl\" href=\"/blog\">Read Our Latest Articles →</a></div></section></div><footer class=\"bg-[#0a1128] text-white pt-24 pb-20 md:pb-12 border-t border-brand-800 relative overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 opacity-5\" style=\"background-image:url(&#x27;https://www.transparenttextures.com/patterns/carbon-fibre.png&#x27;)\"></div><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 relative z-10 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-16 lg:gap-8\"><div class=\"space-y-6\"><a class=\"flex items-center gap-3\" href=\"/\"><div class=\"relative flex items-center justify-center w-12 h-12 bg-brand-900 rounded-xl shadow-lg border border-white/10\"><span class=\"text-2xl\">🛡️</span></div><div class=\"flex flex-col justify-center\"><span class=\"font-extrabold text-2xl tracking-tight leading-none text-white\">batyspestcontrol</span><span class=\"font-bold text-xs tracking-[0.2em] text-accent-500 uppercase mt-0.5\">Pest Control</span></div></a><p class=\"text-surface-400 text-sm leading-relaxed pr-4\">We provide fast, reliable, and eco-friendly pest control services nationwide. Available 24/7 for all your residential and commercial needs.</p><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 text-surface-400 text-sm\"><span class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"text-accent-500\">✓</span> Licensed</span><span class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"text-accent-500\">✓</span> Insured</span><span class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"text-accent-500\">✓</span> Bonded</span></div></div><div><h4 class=\"text-white font-bold mb-8 text-lg\">Our Services</h4><ul class=\"space-y-4 text-sm text-surface-400\"><li><a class=\"hover:text-accent-400 hover:translate-x-1 transition-all flex items-center gap-3\" href=\"/termite-treatment\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 text-[10px]\">■</span> Termite Treatment</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-accent-400 hover:translate-x-1 transition-all flex items-center gap-3\" href=\"/rodent-control\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 text-[10px]\">■</span> Rodent Control</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-accent-400 hover:translate-x-1 transition-all flex items-center gap-3\" href=\"/bed-bug-treatment\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 text-[10px]\">■</span> Bed Bug Treatment</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-accent-400 hover:translate-x-1 transition-all flex items-center gap-3\" href=\"/ant-control-services\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 text-[10px]\">■</span> Ant &amp; Roach Control</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-accent-400 hover:translate-x-1 transition-all flex items-center gap-3\" href=\"/mosquito-control\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 text-[10px]\">■</span> Mosquito Control</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-accent-400 hover:translate-x-1 transition-all flex items-center gap-3\" href=\"/services\"><span class=\"text-brand-500 text-[10px]\">■</span> View All Services</a></li></ul></div><div><h4 class=\"text-white font-bold mb-8 text-lg\">Quick Links</h4><ul 